# Global ignore rules, applied across every knowledge source.
# Same syntax as .gitignore. Per-source .gitignore and .knowledgeignore
# files (anywhere inside a source folder) are ALSO respected automatically
# -- this file is only for rules you want everywhere, regardless of source.
#
# Copy this to .knowledgeignore at the project root to activate it.

# Personal / sensitive
**/private/
**/*.secret.*

# Large binary/media that slips past extension filtering in odd folders
*.zip
*.tar.gz
*.mp4
*.mov
*.csv
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.png
*.json
